"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also 10, in two places.       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqay~aA^ato","text_ar":"تَقَيَّاَتْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She addressed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"presented, herself to her husband, and threw herself upon him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or, accord. to Lth,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she affected languor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"languidness, to her husband, and threw herself upon him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but in the opinion of Az, the verb with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"q","text_ar":"ق"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sense is a mistranscription, and is correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tfy~A^t","text_ar":"تفيّات"},{"kind":"text","text":", [q. v.,] with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]}}